author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Oman's Bank Sohar Q1 Profit Rises
text:
April 15 (Reuters) - BANK SOHAR:
* Q1 NET PROFIT AFTER TAX 8.9 MILLION RIALS VERSUS 6 MILLION RIALS YEAR AGO
* Q1 OPERATING INCOME 21.8 MILLION RIALS VERSUS 15.3 MILLION RIALS YEAR AGO
* AS OF END-MARCH 2018 NET LOANS AND ADVANCES STAND AT 2.17 BILLION RIALS, UP 13.52 PERCENT YEAR-OVER-YEAR
* AS OF END-MARCH 2018 DEPOSITS FROM CUSTOMERS STAND AT 1.66 BILLION RIALS, DOWN 1.56 PERCENT YEAR-OVER-YEAR Source:( bit.ly/2HD9TPq ) Further company coverage:
